Package: artool
Type: Package
Title: (Response-)Adaptive Randomization Routine for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yevgen Ryeznik, Alex Sverdlov
Maintainer: Yevgen Ryeznik <yevgen.ryeznik@gmail.com>
Description: Package implements different adaptive randomization strategies for clinical trials:
    restricted randomization (RR), covariate-adaptive randomization (CAR), 
    response-adaptive randomization (RAR), covariate-adaptive response-adaptive (CARA) 
    randomization. 
License: GPL (>= 2.0)
Depends: Rcpp (>= 0.12.9),
         shiny (>= 1.0.0),
         tidyverse (>= 1.1.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.10)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: GNU make
